  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CArmor Purge\uFF1E (When this Digimon would be deleted,
    you may trash the top card of this Digimon to prevent that deletion.)[When Digivolving]
    Suspend 1 of your opponent's Digimon for each Tamer you have in play. Then, up
    to 3 of your opponent's suspended Digimon get -5000 DP for the turn."
